      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAV REIKO (1) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (29.40) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 515m. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Can make it two on the bounce. ACCREDITED (4) is better than last start when seventh (30.11) in a NG at Wentworth Park over 520m. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Boasts three wins from four starts out of this box. Cannot be taken lightly. KEEP ROLLING (2) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (29.78) in a Mix 3/4 at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Can measure up. NEO DEVERE (6) form at this course and distance reads well.",
